<body id="mercury_bulb___removal">

    <h1 class="title topictitle1" id="ariaid-title1">Mercury bulb - Removal</h1>

    
    <div class="body taskbody"><p class="shortdesc">Removal of the <em class="ph i"><span class="ph">Mercury bulb</span></em>.</p>

        <ol class="ol steps"><li class="li step">
                <span class="ph cmd">Shut off power to light fixture at the circuit breaker.</span>
            </li>
<li class="li step">
                <span class="ph cmd">To open the <em class="ph i"><span class="ph">External Light</span></em> (see item 4 in
                        <a class="xref" href="#mercury_bulb___removal__Ground_Shelter_Front">Figure 1</a>) remove the
                    stainless-steel screws (see item 1 in <a class="xref" href="#mercury_bulb___removal__External_light">Figure 2</a>).</span>
                
                    <div class="fig fignone" id="mercury_bulb___removal__Ground_Shelter_Front"><span class="figcap"><span class="fig--title-label">Figure 1. </span>Ground Shelter Front</span>
                        
                        <img class="image" src="../images/ICN-ACTA-AA-XX-X-XXX-A-D2714-06512-A-A-1.png" height="588" width="473" />
                        <dl class="dl">
                            
                                <dt class="dt dlterm">1</dt>

                                <dd class="dd"><span class="ph">Fire Alarm Beacon
                        (amber)</span></dd>

                            
                            
                                <dt class="dt dlterm">2</dt>

                                <dd class="dd"><span class="ph">Fire Alarm Beacon (red)</span></dd>

                            
                            
                                <dt class="dt dlterm">3</dt>

                                <dd class="dd"><span class="ph">Fire Alarm Bell</span></dd>

                            
                            
                                <dt class="dt dlterm">4</dt>

                                <dd class="dd"><span class="ph">External Light</span></dd>

                            
                            
                                <dt class="dt dlterm">5</dt>

                                <dd class="dd"><span class="ph">Motion Detector</span></dd>

                            
                        </dl>

                    </div>

                    <div class="fig fignone" id="mercury_bulb___removal__External_light"><span class="figcap"><span class="fig--title-label">Figure 2. </span>External light</span>
                        
                        <img class="image" src="../images/ICN-ACTA-AA-XX-X-XXX-A-D2714-06583-A-A-1.png" />
                        <dl class="dl">
                            
                                <dt class="dt dlterm">1</dt>

                                <dd class="dd">Screws</dd>

                            
                            
                                <dt class="dt dlterm">2</dt>

                                <dd class="dd">Bulb</dd>

                            
                        </dl>

                    </div>

                
            </li>
<li class="li step">
                <span class="ph cmd">Remove the <em class="ph i"><span class="ph">Mercury bulb</span></em> (see item 2 in
                        <a class="xref" href="#mercury_bulb___removal__External_light">Figure 2</a>) by rotating the bulb
                    in anti-clock wise direction.</span>
            </li>
</ol>

    </div>

